ith immunosuppressive or myelosuppressive agents should be avoided if possible.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/52660/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Secukinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Belimumab, More', '', 1767369485);
